=== intltool 0.16 ===

2002-02-25  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* NEWS: Notes for 0.16 release.
	* configure.in: Bump version.

	* tests/cases/Makefile.am:
	* tests/results/Makefile.am:
	Add new test cases so they end up in the tarball.

